<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Re-engagement Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #666;
    }
    a {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://thecapitalhub.in/static/media/logo-white.c4e4dacf1f6283c93e11.png" alt="Company Logo" style="max-width: 400px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h2>Hi <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</h2>
    <p>It’s been over 30 days since your last post. We understand that you’ve been busy, but your followers and team are eager to hear what’s new with your startup!</p>
    
    <p>Don’t let your company go silent—keep your community engaged and show them your progress. Posting updates is a great way to keep your brand visible and active.</p>

    <p>Click below to get back to your dashboard and share your latest update:</p>
    
    <p><a href="<%= dashboardLink %>">Post an Update</a></p>
    
    <p>We’re here to support you if you need any help along the way. Let’s get your startup back on track!</p>

    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The CapitalHub Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
